# 📊 Power BI Dashboard Collection for Windows

**Professional data visualization and business intelligence tool — transform raw data into actionable insights!** Power BI Dashboard Collection is a comprehensive Windows application that packages pre-built dashboard templates, data connectors, and visualization tools into a single executable. Create stunning interactive reports, monitor KPIs in real-time, and share insights across your organization.

Whether you're a data analyst, business manager, or student learning BI, this collection provides everything you need to master data storytelling with Microsoft Power BI.

> **Note:** This tool complements Microsoft Power BI Desktop (free version required). All templates and connectors are open-source or freely available for commercial use.

---

