## 🖥️ System Requirements

| Component | Minimum | Recommended |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| **OS** | Windows 10 (64-bit) | Windows 11 (64-bit) |
| **Processor** | 1.6 GHz dual-core | 2.5 GHz quad-core or better |
| **RAM** | 4 GB | 16 GB or more |
| **Storage** | 2 GB free space | 5+ GB for datasets |
| **Display** | 1366x768 | 1920x1080 or higher |
| **Power BI** | Power BI Desktop (free) | Latest version |
| **Internet** | Required for cloud connectors | Broadband recommended |

---

## 🚀 Quick Start Guide

**Step 1:** Download and install Microsoft Power BI Desktop (free from Microsoft Store)

**Step 2:** Download `.exe` from the link above

**Step 3:** Run the executable and choose installation folder

**Step 4:** Launch Power BI Desktop

**Step 5:** Browse templates from the integrated gallery:
- File → Open from Gallery
- Browse by category
- Click "Download & Open"

**Step 6:** Connect your data source and customize

