## 🔧 Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| **Templates not loading** | Check internet connection, update Power BI |
| **Slow performance** | Reduce data volume, optimize DAX, use aggregations |
| **Connector errors** | Verify credentials, check firewall settings |
| **Visuals missing** | Install custom visuals from marketplace |
| **Refresh failures** | Check gateway configuration, data source availability |
| **Publishing errors** | Verify workspace permissions, file size limits |

