## ❓ Frequently Asked Questions

**Q: Is Power BI Desktop free?**  
A: Yes, Microsoft Power BI Desktop is completely free. Power BI Pro (for sharing) requires a subscription.

**Q: Do I need coding skills?**  
A: No, the drag-and-drop interface makes it accessible. DAX formulas are optional for advanced users.

**Q: Can I use these templates commercially?**  
A: Yes, all templates are licensed for commercial use.

**Q: How often are templates updated?**  
A: New templates are added monthly, with quarterly major updates.

**Q: Does it work with Excel?**  
A: Yes, seamless integration with Excel files and Power Pivot models.

**Q: Can I share dashboards with non-Power BI users?**  
A: Yes, export to PDF, PowerPoint, or embed in websites.

**Q: Is there a cloud version?**  
A: These templates work with Power BI Service for cloud publishing.

